patthana8.68:1.1: Narūpāvacaraṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca narūpāvacaro dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā … tīṇi.
patthana8.68:2.1: Nanarūpāvacaraṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nanarūpāvacaro dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā … tīṇi.
patthana8.68:3.1: Narūpāvacarañca nanarūpāvacarañca dhammaṃ paṭicca narūpāvacaro dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā … tīṇi. (Saṃkhittaṃ.)
patthana8.68:4.1: Hetuyā nava, ārammaṇe cattāri, adhipatiyā pañca …pe… aññamaññe cha …pe… purejāte āsevane dve …pe… avigate nava.
